reviewText: A Funny flick from back in the day. It has been a while since I saw  it. Last time was at a Drive In. Now thanks to "Modern Technology" I can be for watchin' it anytime I wants to!
An old classic movie full of action and some very sexy women
This was a surprise for my husband who wanted to see this movie when it came out on TV many, many years ago. He was very happy and we can't wait to set up a VCR to watch it!
